<br />\n但人地每日涼冷氣  坐係到<br />\n你就日日行下跑下搬下十粒鐘<br />\n十幾年後會點  老左會點<br />\n到四十幾五十歲  日日返到屋企都要貼住d止痛貼？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:07:44.000Z","msg":"median would not count the outlier in fact, I think you misunderstand median as mean"},{"pid":"d2d59d94814c5fa853e702360d4a68ff90174ce8","tid":1163811,"uid":38006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:23:55.000Z","msg":"成個社會都係分級數嘅，班on9仔以此為榮都冇辦法。<br />\n十年八年後睇下自己係邊個位咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班小學雞屌扑叔，扑叔都唔會少條毛，照舊坐頭等玩遊輪。<br />\n冇用公子有班小學雞fans所以叫做搵到個錢就扮哂為基層家庭發聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班撐冇用公子嘅學生哥好快d學你偶像去打機玩直播啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就黎暑假，好快會係唔同既麥當勞見到冇用公子嘅粉絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad721b1573f1d3368582d1c2a4cadbe5f8cc73a","tid":1163811,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"survivorship bias 同hasty generalization  無用公子同佢啲打手死忠撚知係咩<br />\n講到明話「讀書無用」都可以扮無講過, 無恥過民建聯啦"},{"pid":"8217efa01d84ef93c4cec291b83cf7076563bce0","tid":1163811,"uid":18540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xHZ57Dc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxHZ57Dc.png&h=cedf6a52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人有睇過呢條片？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條片係youtube睇唔返<br />\n想知係咪真"},{"pid":"32258c439756f8cfacc8a89211e6e6cffe900d14","tid":1163811,"uid":91584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8217efa01d84ef93c4cec291b83cf7076563bce0","tid":1163811,"uid":18540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img sr